viewData.name: ASUS 13.3" ZenBook 13 UX331FAL Laptop
viewData.short_description: Buy ASUS 13.3" ZenBook 13 UX331FAL Laptop featuring 1.8 GHz Intel Core i7-8565U Quad-Core, 8GB LPDDR3 | 256GB M.2 SSD 13.3" 1920 x 1080 WideView Display. Review ASUS
viewData.long_description: The 13.3" ZenBook 13 UX331FAL Laptop from Asus is a thin and lightweight system designed to keep up with you throughout the day while you're on-the-go. Specs-wise, it's built with a 1.8 GHz Intel Core i7-8565U quad-core processor, 8GB of LPDDR3 RAM, and a 256GB M.2 SSD. Its 13.3" display, driven by integrated Intel UHD graphics, features a 1920 x 1080 Full HD resolution and has wide 178Â° viewing angles with ultra-slim NanoEdge bezels. Other integrated features include USB Type-A and Type-C ports, an HDMI port, a microSDXC card reader, a webcam, microphones, speakers, and a 3.5mm combo audio jack. The operating system installed is Windows 10 (64-Bit).
